{"blocks":[{"key":"11u6f","text":"Once the AFC has finished the extraction, combine the first three fractions and discard or store the fourth.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8cg5r","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"39rs7","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7ep4f","text":"The fourth fraction contains primarily protein and a very low concentration of EVs.","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"matq","text":"Discard the used qEVsingle column and clean the central well with a kimwipe delicate task wipe.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3e6im","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"e5ft8","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3v4oh","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"d657e","text":"Ensure the central well is completely dry before next use.","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"b4cj7","text":"Repeat steps 12 -18 for additional samples.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"d59p4","text":"Remove peristaltic pump tubing from below the column mount by removing the plastic cover on the peristaltic pump.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"43qqf","text":"Flush plastic tubing with   filtered water using a 10 mL syringe and replace plastic tubing on AFC.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":26,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"30ttq","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":1,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"88vpj","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"amount","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"amount":"5","error":false,"guid":"CD4D8FF0250511EDB9E1C9D787E546F9","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"unit":2}},"1":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"f0tf8","text":"This will prevent buildup of salt crystals in the tubing between uses.","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4ll4v","text":"Combine fractions 1-3 and immediately process for use on TRPS, store short term (1-2 weeks) at  , or store long term (\u003e 2 weeks) at  .","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":95,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":132,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"bfjcj","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"F7B26040250511EDB9E1C9D787E546F9","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"-20","unit":10}},"1":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"A716F3A027B011ED88D32D3BAF07542D","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"-81","unit":10}}}}
